originalText.text: After a few years of searching for the right stylist in New York, I was finally blessed to find Angie. On my first visit, Angie was honest and professional in letting me know my hair was not quite long enough to execute the style I was hoping for. She touched up my hair and recommended I come back in some time. She refused my offer to pay her for the consultation and services she provided. I came back in her recommended time frame, and have been grateful for every visit since. Haircuts are stressful for me ðŸ˜… but Angie makes it a point to put you at ease and make the experience as comfortable as possible. I have gotten compliments left and right after each cut. Overall, as a stylist and a human being, I would rate Angie a 10/10 :).

originalText.text: I've had a number of haircuts I wasn't satisfied with over the years - I found Angie after trying quite a few stylists in NYC. She's easy to talk to, and will help you talk through what you want if you're not sure what exactly to ask for (like me). I've been booking with Angie for over 3 years now. Cozy atmosphere and a drink on the side make for a great experience.

originalText.text: Angie is an absolute legend. Every cut and style is a great value because it grows in extremely nicely. I can go sometimes go months on a single haircut and it looks great the whole time. I highly recommend her to any guy who cares about looking his best!
